<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Your AbyRide Reservation Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    /* Your full styles included here */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #47B2E4 0%, #293751 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 40px 30px;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
  
    

    .header::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -50%;
      left: -50%;
      width: 200%;
      height: 200%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
      animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes pulse {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.5; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.1); opacity: 0.8; }
    }

    .header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .header p {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

        .header img {
          max-width:200px;
          margin-bottom: 20px;
          height:100px;
        }


    .content {
      padding: 30px;
    }

    .welcome-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #293751;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .welcome-section p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .status-badge {
      background: #47B2E4;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 25px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .reservation-details h3,
    .followup-section h3,
    .footer h3 {
      color: #293751;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #47B2E4;
    }

    .details-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .detail-card {
      background: #f4f8fc;
      border: 1px solid #d3e9f8;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }

    .detail-card strong {
      display: block;
      color: #293751;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .detail-card span {
      color: #47B2E4;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .followup-section {
      background: #e9f6fd;
      border-left: 5px solid #47B2E4;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .followup-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #333;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #f0f4f9;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      border-top: 1px solid #d0e2f2;
    }

    .footer p {
      color: #333;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .footer a {
      color: #47B2E4;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 10px;
        border-radius: 15px;
      }

      .header {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .content {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .details-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
      <img src="https://aspirebridgerwanda.org/abyride-logo.png" alt="Abyride Logo" />
      <h1>ðŸš— Abyride Reservation Received</h1>
      <p>Thank you for applying to join our platform</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="welcome-section">
        <h2>Hello {{firstName}} {{lastName}}!</h2>
        <p>Thank you for choosing AbyRide for your transportation needs.</p>
        <p>We're excited to provide you with a premium ride experience.</p>
     </div>

      <div class="reservation-details">
        <h3>ðŸ“‹ Your Reservation Details</h3>
        <div class="details-grid">
            <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Reservation Number</strong>
            <span>{{reservationNumber}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Pickup Location</strong>
            <span>{{pickup}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Dropoff Location</strong>
            <span>{{dropoff}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Scheduled Time</strong>
            <span>{{scheduledDateTime}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Distance</strong>
            <span>{{distance}}</span>
          </div>
          <div class="detail-card">
            <strong>Total Price</strong>
            <span>{{price}}</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

     <div class="followup-section">
  <h3>ðŸ•’ What Happens Next?</h3>
  <p>We are currently reviewing your reservation request. One of our team members will reach out to you shortly to confirm the availability and discuss the payment process.</p>
  <p>Please ensure your contact information is up to date and reachable.</p>
  <p>If you wish to cancel your reservation, you can do so here:</p>
  <p><a href="{{cancelUrl}}" style="color: #e63946; text-decoration: underline;">Cancel My Reservation</a></p>
</div>

    </div>
  <div class="footer">
            <h3>Need Assistance?</h3>
            <p>Our support team is available 24/7 to help with any questions</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:support@abyride.com">support@abyride.com</a> | <a href="tel:+1234567890">+1 (234) 567-890</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9;">
                Thank you for choosing Abyride LLC - Your trusted transportation partner<br>
                <em>Excellence in Motion, Service in Every Mile</em>
            </p>
        </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
